statcounter url www statcounter com commercial yes type of site web traffic analysis registration not required for basic access alexa rank 214 january 2013 update 1 current status active statcounter is a web traffic analysis tool access to basic services is free and advanced services can cost between 9 and 119 a month 2 the company is based in dublin the statistics from statcounter are used to compute web usage share for example 3 statcounter statistics are directly derived from hits not unique visitors from 3 million sites using statcounter totaling more than 15 billion hits per month 4 no artificial weightings are used the company was founded by dublin man aodhan cullen born in 1983 at the age of 16 he remains the ceo of statcounter cullen received the internet hero award at the 2008 eircom golden spider awards 5 he was also named the 2007 businessweek young european entrepreneur of the year 6 7 in 2008 the company surpassed two million members globally edit references statcounter com site info alexa internet http www alexa com siteinfo statcounter com retrieved 2012 08 02 kyle lacy 2011 twitter marketing for dummies john wiley and sons p 160 93 statcounter global stats statcounter http gs statcounter com retrieved 2012 08 22 statcounter statistics methodology statcounter http gs statcounter com faq methodology retrieved 12 january 2011 http www techcentral ie article aspx id 12820 http www accessmylibrary com coms2 summary 0286 31981753 itm john kennedy 2007 08 03 the friday interview aodhan cullen statcounter siliconrepublic com http www siliconrepublic com careers item 8521 the friday interview aodha retrieved 2012 09 21 this world wide web related article is a stub you can help wikipedia by expanding it v t e 